===體積===
這顆恆星的半徑約為太陽半徑的1,287-1,535倍（5.98到7.14天文單位），半徑達895,108,500至1,067,592,500公里。<ref name="torres2013"/>其體積是如此之大，若將天蠍座AH放在太陽系的中心，它的表面將超過木星軌道（5.204267天文單位，778,547,200公里）<ref name=horizons>{{cite web|last = Yeomans|first = Donald K.|date = 2006-07-13|url = http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/horizons.cgi?find_body=1&body_group=mb&sstr=5|title = HORIZONS Web-Interface for Jupiter Barycenter (Major Body=5)|publisher = [[JPL_Horizons_On-Line_Ephemeris_System|JPL Horizons On-Line Ephemeris System]]|accessdate = 2007-08-08|archive-date = 2019-01-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190109070123/https://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/?horizons|dead-url = no}} – Select "Ephemeris Type: Orbital Elements", "Time Span: 2000-01-01 12:00 to 2000-01-02". ("Target Body: Jupiter Barycenter" and "Center: Sun" should be defaulted to.)</ref>，並且接近[[土星|土星]]軌道（9.5820172天文單位，1,433,449,370公里）<ref name="horizons_1_6">{{cite web | last=Yeomans | first=Donald K. | date=2006-07-13 | url=http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/horizons.cgi?find_body=1&body_group=mb&sstr=6 | title=HORIZONS Web-Interface for Saturn Barycenter (Major Body=6) | publisher=[[JPL_Horizons_On-Line_Ephemeris_System|JPL Horizons On-Line Ephemeris System]] | accessdate=2007-08-08 | archive-date=2013-05-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501170543/http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/horizons.cgi?find_body=1&body_group=mb&sstr=6 | dead-url=no }} – Select "Ephemeris Type: Orbital Elements", "Time Span: 2000-01-01 12:00 to 2000-01-02". ("Target Body: Saturn Barycenter" and "Center: Sun" should be defaulted to.)</ref>光環繞這顆恆星的赤道一周需時5.21至6.21小時，而光環繞太陽赤道一周僅需時14.5秒。<ref name=sse>{{cite web 
